      "instruction": "<p>Top the <strong>ciabatta base[s]</strong> with the <strong>sliced tomato</strong>,<strong> torn mozzarella </strong>and<strong> grated cheese</strong></p><p>Tear over your <strong>'Nduja</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and drizzle over<strong> </strong>most of<strong> </strong>your<strong> honey </strong>(you'll use the rest later!) with a pinch of<strong> pepper</strong></p><p>Place a <strong>ciabatta lid </strong>on top – this is your<strong> 'Nduja ciabatta</strong></p>",
