      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a generous drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium heat</p><p>Once hot, add the<strong> 'Nduja ciabatta </strong>and cover with a smaller pan</p><p>Add a heavy weight (eg. several tins) to the top pan and cook for 4-5 min per side, checking occasionally or until the ciabatta is golden and the cheese has melted – this is your <strong>'Nduja hot honey cheese toastie</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
