    {
      "instruction": "<p>Wash your <strong>salad </strong>and pat dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Combine the <strong>remaining white wine vinegar</strong> and the <strong>remaining honey </strong>in a large bowl with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>pepper </strong>– this is your <strong>dressing</strong></p><p>Add the<strong> salad </strong>and toss<strong> </strong>– this is your <strong>dressed salad</strong></p>",
