      "instruction": "<p>Cut the <strong>'Nduja hot honey cheese toastie </strong>in half<strong> </strong>and serve<strong> </strong>with the<strong> herby fries</strong>, <strong>dressed salad </strong>and <strong>garlic dip </strong>to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
